JOSI:
3:15 to sub-3 is a 15-minute improvement — ambitious but doable with 4 months if your base is solid. You've been consistent, which is the most important factor. The plan will build through base into a specific build phase with tempo and threshold work targeting that 4:15/km pace. Key question: are you able to train 5-6 days a week? That volume will matter for the jump from 3:15 to sub-3.
